            <p>Many adults struggle to make time for Quran study due to busy schedules filled with work, education, and household responsibilities. However, with the right strategies, it's possible to incorporate Quran study into daily life. Dar Arqam offers practical and flexible learning solutions, including online Quran classes designed for busy adults. Whether it's using post-Fajr hours, integrating Quran sessions into office breaks, or listening to recitations during commutes, Dar Arqam ensures that Quran learning fits seamlessly into your lifestyle.</p>

